{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"838c02137b","title":"关于铁路的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6fe26674d4","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"838c02137b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949.10-1957.12）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76fd1ca441","type":"paragraph","text":"关于铁路的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"146182726f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九四九年十月）解放军打到那里，我何的铁路修到那里。","index":1,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"53853f0531","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自膝××在全国铁路会上的，","index":2,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"e0ed008d92","type":"paragraph","text":"见《人民日报》一九四九年十月二十九日）","index":3,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"ec39339998","type":"paragraph","text":"给徐悲鸿的一封信悲满先生：","index":4,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"64f6fc4996","type":"paragraph","text":"表示敬悉，写了一张，未知可用否？","index":5,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"596166174f","type":"paragraph","text":"顺教琪","index":6,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"50e0a6628d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛东","index":7,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"1f56561e36","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年十一月二十九日（注：新中国阿刚成立，徐悲鸿先生敬请堂大袖","index":8,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"f1f8b413ba","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席为中央美术学院题宇，此为主席复信。）关于一九五零年军队参加生产建设工作的指示","index":9,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"38b93a6c33","type":"paragraph","text":"（中央人民政府人民革命重事委会颁发）","index":10,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"74fadbc0ba","type":"paragraph","text":"人民解放战争已在全国范圈内取得基本的胜利，人民解放重除在几个战线上必须专心致志追开残敌以党全功之外，已有大量重队进入整，或不人即将进人整割。人民政治协商会共同网中规定：“中华人民共和国的重队，在和平时间，在不妨碍重事任务的条件下，应有计划的参加农业和工业的生产，帮助国家的散建工作。”这里给了我人民重队除了保卫国防、巩固治安和加强整训这些体大任务以外的一个光荣而巨大的任务。因此，人民革命军事委员会号召全罩，除作战和服勤务者而外，应当负担一部分生产任务，使我人民解放重不仅是一支国防审，而且是一支生产军，借以协同全国人民克服长期战争所遗留下来的困难，加速新民主主义的建散。","index":11,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"3e6efe7f72","type":"paragraph","text":"这一生产任务是必须而且可能实现的","index":12,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"},{"id":"050215402e","type":"paragraph","text":"这一生产任务之所以必须实现，是由于国内外反动派所发动的长期的反对中国人民的战争，给了人民以严重的炎难，给了经济以严重的破坏。我何今天将革命战争进行到底，","index":13,"publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b"}],"page":{"id":"66ff1405b4","publicationId":"9646ca98-820c-44ef-b8ca-c656fd59b7fd","articleId":"838c02137b","start":7,"end":7}}}},"__N_SSG":true}